            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-9032cb01cc4698e4-f09fcd twpub-9032cb01cc4698e4-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
